OL,3,CJersey inflation more than halves but
OL,4,Ctobacco and leisure prices rocket
OL,6,FInflation has more than halved in
OL,7,FJersey over a year.
OL,9,FThe figure now stands at 5%, compared
OL,10,Fto 10.9% in June 2023 and the 30-year
OL,11,Frecord-high of 12.7% in January 2023.
OL,13,FThe most recent rate is also slightly
OL,14,Fbelow Guernsey where prices are rising
OL,15,Fby 5.3%.
OL,17,FHowever, despite the overall rate that
OL,18,Fprices are rising by slowing down in
OL,19,FJersey, some sectors continue to see
OL,20,Fbig increases.
