OL,3,CJersey inflation more than halves but
OL,4,Ctobacco and leisure prices rocket
OL,6,FThe cost of tobacco went up by 12.2%
OL,7,Fin the last year while leisure
OL,8,Fservices will set you back an extra
OL,9,F10.7%.
OL,11,FThe price of power and housing also
OL,12,Fsaw notable above-inflation rises at
OL,13,F8.8% and 7.3% respectively.
OL,15,FThat housing figure is still driven by
OL,16,Fthe high cost of mortgage interest
OL,17,Fpayments, although this has slowed in
OL,18,Fthe last quarter.
